{"tid":1767062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京加工廠發生爆炸  1死2失蹤","createTime":"2019-12-03T04:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T06:34:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c2afb095a9a5ae5762ee3dff6122b8dd3810d8","tid":1767062,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"北京順義區牛欄山鎮京日東大食品有限公司一間加工豆餡廠房發生爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今天（3日）凌晨3時左右，消防接報後馬上前往現場。3時40分，現場明火已撲滅。目前11人送醫救治，2人失聯，1人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n市區兩級事後已迅速啟動應急處置機制，目前正調查爆炸原因。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，此前該公司曾因使用5台X射線裝置，未辦理輻射安全許可證被當地環境保護局罰款。<br />\n<br />\n目前，事故原因正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1651846/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%A0%86%E7%BE%A9%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%88%BF%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8-%E5%B7%B2%E8%87%B41%E6%AD%BB2%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2aa51a81ec1a5f0377fdea9a46b45598d1b68496","tid":1767062,"uid":11454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"又做唔住呃保險"},{"pid":"07b7d0a4924f3231e526853864da422a0eca98ee","tid":1767062,"uid":81140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"失聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a0fb131692dffa94d007b86dd67ffdabd482f3","tid":1767062,"uid":124616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"9a624369f0dff553800255d854fdfa138ccbaf72","tid":1767062,"uid":172485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"爆炸當食生菜 鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703deae81559606d75145c842ff78a60636e6e65","tid":1767062,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"食品公司都可以大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90d7ff47447